{"tid":1211773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［ 合 集 ］警 隊 暴 力 打 壓 示 威 者","createTime":"2019-06-12T16:31:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T14:40:09.000Z","uid":125029,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a87e3d25e09382d8b315abb1d51c60d604e0d244","tid":1211773,"uid":125029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:31:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我總結左幾個post既內容，等大家一次過睇晒黑警有幾咁仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n濫用權力，搜9學生哥身，叫佢哋一字排開：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hBeheL1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhBeheL1.png&h=569f0998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n恰9阿婆，暴力清場：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gYqL740.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgYqL740.png&h=50aeb9e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/2847293785311667/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkon9agroup%2Fpermalink%2F2847293785311667%2F&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgv8RCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=b70bf750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/2847293785311667/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n亂棍毆打手無寸鐵嘅婦孺：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KPs6Sx2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKPs6Sx2.png&h=62939d76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/watch/?v=1140898209445246&amp;_rdr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1140898209445246%26_rdr&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgv8RCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=bfeb8e0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/watch/?v=1140898209445246&amp;_rdr</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n強行拖行女示威者，令其內衣外露：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EPa8msr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEPa8msr.png&h=c6af7e28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在未有警告情況之下，開槍射擊示威者：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PB1b3F9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPB1b3F9.png&h=e1030dc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2V00W1c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2V00W1c.png&h=cb514793&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n挑釁示威者，詆毁普世價值：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fcAsB1V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfcAsB1V.png&h=134ff8e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A5qcN8B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA5qcN8B.png&h=e6385996&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HKVYB2LRACA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHKVYB2LRACA&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgv8RCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=9e71c496\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HKVYB2LRACA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n襲擊記者，踐踏新聞自由：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POJmGvH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOJmGvH.png&h=d166c8b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%9D%87%E7%89%87-%E5%95%86%E5%8F%B0%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E8%A1%A8%E6%98%8E%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD-%E4%BB%8D%E9%81%AD%E6%8F%AE%E8%AD%A6%E6%A3%8D%E7%B2%97%E6%9A%B4%E6%8E%A8%E6%92%9E-%E8%AD%A6-%E8%A8%98%E4%BD%A0%E8%80%81%E6%AF%8D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%259D%2587%25E7%2589%2587-%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%258F%25B0%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BB%25BD-%25E4%25BB%258D%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%258F%25AE%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25A3%258D%25E7%25B2%2597%25E6%259A%25B4%25E6%258E%25A8%25E6%2592%259E-%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E8%25A8%2598%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E8%2580%2581%25E6%25AF%258D%2F&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgv8RCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=81fdcc46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%259D%2587%25E7%2589%2587-%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%258F%25B0%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BB%25BD-%25E4%25BB%258D%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%258F%25AE%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25A3%258D%25E7%25B2%2597%25E6%259A%25B4%25E6%258E%25A8%25E6%2592%259E-%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E8%25A8%2598%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E8%2580%2581%25E6%25AF%258D%2F&h=3b9a48e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%9D%87%E7%89%87-%E5%95%86%E5%8F%B0%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E8%A1%A8%E6%98%8E%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD-%E4%BB%8D%E9%81%AD%E6%8F%AE%E8%AD%A6%E6%A3%8D%E7%B2%97%E6%9A%B4%E6%8E%A8%E6%92%9E-%E8%AD%A6-%E8%A8%98%E4%BD%A0%E8%80%81%E6%AF%8D/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">屌你老母，班黑警簡直無法無天，有恃無恐，老弱婦孺都照打，完全唔放香港人在眼內。我話你哋知，警察既責任係保護市民，即使我哋做咩都好，你都唔應該開槍，佢哋班仆街依家竟然向當權者倒戈，幫佢哋手打壓市民，一定唔可以放過。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"1ce2a0e6b79bf5bb3974ffec81a78567f500aaae","tid":1211773,"uid":125029,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:31:31.000Z","msg":"經過今日依一戰，大家都知道警察係唔會留手，佢哋有幾多催淚彈就掟幾多，連企喺一邊咩都冇做過都照打。所以，我哋都唔使錫住佢哋，下次行動一定要再升級，準備更多物資。我哋一定要攻入立法會佔領議事廳，唔俾林鄭條仆街通過送中條例。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97c5c7de8e18dae84386d889cb10685895f777d","tid":1211773,"uid":258566,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:32:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1747dbe62b5a6e2d601d8f9fc0645f7696a62c41","tid":1211773,"uid":125029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c97c5c7de8e18dae84386d889cb10685895f777d","tid":121177